{"tid":2051152,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"[港台電視] 出位家族 Stacey Dooley Sleeps Over  逢星期四 2130-2230","createTime":"2020-06-04T14:30:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-09T17:12:41.000Z","uid":30,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"cfefe499e14fb7a40ac4dcb4dd4587dc5df2ffd8","tid":2051152,"uid":30,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T14:30:34.000Z","msg":"出位家族 Stacey Dooley Sleeps Over<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.rthk.hk/assets/rthk/images/programme/dtt31/staceydooleysleepsover/8915_programme_slider_44532_0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rthk.hk%2Fassets%2Frthk%2Fimages%2Fprogramme%2Fdtt31%2Fstaceydooleysleepsover%2F8915_programme_slider_44532_0.jpg&h=67db7040&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一連六集節目，電視節目主持暨製作人史黛斯．杜莉會帶領觀眾由核心外圍走到核心內圍，深入採訪六個另類英國家庭的日常生活。史黛斯會在每個家庭留宿72小時，每日陪他們食足三餐之餘，還會一起返工、返學、放狗、按摩、 打獵、夜蒲、參加MMA比賽，務求在三日三夜內揭出他們最不為人知的一面。史黛斯與家庭成員的各種互動，亦帶出各人對關係、金錢、伴侶、性、工作、夢想等等日常生活議題的獨特見解。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n英國地主<br />\n史黛斯會去阿克萊特家族位於沃里克郡鄉郊的莊園大屋留宿。阿克萊特家族家世顯赫，是工業革命時期因開設全球第一間工廠而致富的李察．阿克萊特爵士的直系親屬。史黛斯與他們在打獵、私立學校教育、遺產繼承等議題上各持己見，激起熱烈火花。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.rthk.hk/oldassets/images/rthk/dtt31/staceydooleysleepsover/originals/mfile_8915_683474_7_l.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rthk.hk%2Foldassets%2Fimages%2Frthk%2Fdtt31%2Fstaceydooleysleepsover%2Foriginals%2Fmfile_8915_683474_7_l.jpg&h=9f644f80&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.rthk.hk/oldassets/images/rthk/dtt31/staceydooleysleepsover/originals/mfile_8915_683474_2_l.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rthk.hk%2Foldassets%2Fimages%2Frthk%2Fdtt31%2Fstaceydooleysleepsover%2Foriginals%2Fmfile_8915_683474_2_l.jpg&h=794d84c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.rthk.hk/oldassets/images/rthk/dtt31/staceydooleysleepsover/originals/mfile_8915_683474_3_l.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rthk.hk%2Foldassets%2Fimages%2Frthk%2Fdtt31%2Fstaceydooleysleepsover%2Foriginals%2Fmfile_8915_683474_3_l.jpg&h=968feffa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.rthk.hk/oldassets/images/rthk/dtt31/staceydooleysleepsover/originals/mfile_8915_683474_8_l.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rthk.hk%2Foldassets%2Fimages%2Frthk%2Fdtt31%2Fstaceydooleysleepsover%2Foriginals%2Fmfile_8915_683474_8_l.jpg&h=6e6f140d&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n聲演主持：彭晴<br />\n雙語廣播：粵語/英語 (電視版)<br />\n播放頻道：港台電視31、31A<br />\n播出時間：(首播) 2020年6月11日 星期四 晚上9時半"},{"pid":"4fc092569b17f80dc71821ecdd487569637184cd","tid":2051152,"uid":86449,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T00:55:40.000Z","msg":"留名, 31看世界都有播佢主持D節目<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eddf6ab7e7a459893f4164f75a3f75843230f8f8","tid":2051152,"uid":30,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T13:35:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcc01154fb8f16d43b51ba3a5af53b46e0ea2577","tid":2051152,"uid":30,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T13:35:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3948ed18a66c2ba9c65b9169115ca7c09f6a8e04","tid":2051152,"uid":30,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T13:36:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89c9c1c9e255a347923151a64657c4f1369a6649","tid":2051152,"uid":